snippet.title: Davisson Brothers Band & Amber Lawrence - Greatest Show On Earth (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Written by the Davisson Brothers, Amber Lawrence, and Rob Synder, and produced by Dan Frizsell, “Greatest Show On Earth” was a labor of love with both parties at each end of the world doing their part to get the quality sound to make it a world-class production.  They ended up with over one hundred tracks and eight different acoustic guitar parts with guest musicians, Bryan Sutton, who wrote and played additional guitar, banjo, and mandolin parts. Everyone involved did their part to assist in making the duet as big and powerful as could be to ensure the poignant lyrical message could be heard loud and clear.

“We recommend everyone listening to this at high volume and a lot of bass!  We wish nothing but good to everyone and we hope this brightens someone’s day when they hear it. That’s all this song was meant to do--bring positivity to the world," says Chris Davisson.

A special thank you to the fans that submitted their own videos!

Listen to Greatest Show on Earth now: https://orcd.co/greatestshowonearth
